Merkel Commission Seeks Nuclear Exit by 2021, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-05-29T12:21:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/merkel-commission-seeks-nuclear-exit-by-2021-handelsblatt-says.html
German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s
ethics commission of energy policy advisers is recommending a
nuclear exit by 2021,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing a copy of a
report due to be delivered to Merkel tomorrow.  The commission is “convinced” the nuclear pullout could
be completed “within a decade,” the newspaper cited the report
as saying. The advisory panel will push for a deadline to be set
and enforced, according to Handelsblatt.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at OR
 nkresge@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net  